Package edu.arizona.biosemantics.semanticmarkup.config Description

Contains the base configurations of a Charaparser run. The configurations are Google Guice dependency injection modules. The base configuration are refined by taxongroup in package edu.arizona.biosemantics.semanticmarkup.config.taxongroup.
